b publishing. Y'all can laugh, but what if Jeb Bush goofed on purpose. What's more everyman than typos on your Facebook post?\nJeb Bush has decided to \"activelyexplore\" possibility of being president of \"ournation.\"   Jeb! Space key! Hit it! pic.twitter.com\/EZC2tO2Tj8\n","Title":"Jeb Bush used Facebook to announce he wants to run for president | The Verge","Tags":["web","culture","us-world"]}